以去搵佢<br />\n<br />\n佢自己吹到自己好堅</blockquote><br />\n下年會再去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但拉薩應該變左好多吧...第二次果陣已經全城改造....文化破壞 唉 屌佢老母中共"},{"pid":"34461148aae858831b14238d4ff7f0528631561f","tid":192742,"uid":83217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T06:19:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有間叫驢友唔知乜 係青旅附近 入去食煲仔飯 好食</blockquote><br />\n貴撚到開花</blockquote><br />\n但幾好食 去兩次都有食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n果檔野個創辦人拆左伙, 師傅入左東措樓底開檔, 再有下次可以去搵佢<br />\n<br />\n佢自己吹到自己好堅</blockquote><br />\n下年會再去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但拉薩應該變左好多吧...第二次果陣已經全城改造....文化破壞 唉 屌佢老母中共</blockquote><br />\n差無撚幾, 有D位搞緊新商場囉<br />\n<br />\n不過D青旅冇以前咁好玩了, 再去住單房算"},{"pid":"56d067f70e8cf3e72214081e8b80f8d489eda69d","tid":192742,"uid":49702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T07:08:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WC27w5V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWC27w5V.jpg&h=0d063fd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢間超正 帶左兩班唔同既人食過兩次<br />\nD野好有特色 推介藏式東坡肉"},{"pid":"680b5efdaf1e92732144cbea59e661d2f8039caa","tid":192742,"uid":22430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T08:05:35.000Z","msg":"有間喺老樹嗰邊上樓食嘅 味道唔錯<br />\n有間麻辣燙好出名 你google西藏麻辣燙 都應該搵到 真心好撚好食 嗰時我病到仆街都食哂成兜 勁香又夠味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有一兩間但都係冇記名 對個位置印象濛糊<br />\n記得去食烤肉串 好香又平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92121470df7a4123379bcaf5834f11743d102f2d","tid":192742,"uid":71068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T08:34:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>果時去八成食四川菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啲強國人話西藏人冇飲食文化，係四川師傅將真正嘅食物帶入西藏"},{"pid":"234f4118039f14034afb0b6bbbd0cf79753d8852","tid":192742,"uid":7106